00:31:10.750 --> 00:31:13.840
First is make your postbacks
idempotent.

00:31:13.840 --> 00:31:15.990
This is important because you
want to be able to send the

00:31:15.990 --> 00:31:19.270
transactions over and over
again, have the code check for

00:31:19.270 --> 00:31:20.410
