And make sure that the load and
performance is there and

00:31:43.370 --> 00:31:47.070
looks good before you go live.

00:31:47.070 --> 00:31:49.815
Next is you want to track
everything about payments.

00:31:49.815 --> 00:31:51.670
I cannot stress this enough.

00:31:51.670 --> 00:31:54.550
Any time that someone is in
your payments flow, in the

00:31:54.550 --> 00:31:56.690
funnel, you want to track
everything that they do to

00:31:56.690 --> 00:31:59.010
